<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَأَبْعَدُ مِنْ هَذَا عَنْ السِّحْرِ أَنَّهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَضِيعٌ يُنَادِي بِاللِّسَانِ الْفَصِيحَةِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يُنَزِّهُ عَنْ رَيْبِ الظُّنُونِ عَفِيفَةً<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مُبَرَّأَةً مِنْ كُلِّ سُوءٍ وَرِيبَةِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَقَالَ لأَهْلِ السَّبْتِ كُونُوا إِلَهُنَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قُرُودًا فَكَانُوا عِبْرَةً أَيَّ عِبْرَةِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَصَرَّعَ أَهْلَ الْفِيلِ مِنْ دُونِ بَيْتِهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِطَيْرِ أَبَابِيلٍ صِغَارٍ ضَعِيفَةِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَحْرَقَ رَوْضَ الْجَنَّتَيْنُ عُقُوبَةً<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِكَافٍ وَنُونٍ عِبْرَةً لِلْبَرِيَّةِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يوسف بن مُحَمَّد الصرصري رحمه الله:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مُحَمَّدٌ الْمَبْعُوثُ لِلْخَلْقِ رَحْمَةً<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>يُشَيِّدُ مَا أَوْهَى الضَّلالُ وَيُصْلِحُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَئِنْ سَبَّحَتْ صُمُّ الْجِبَالِ مُجِيبَةً<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لِدَاوُدَ أَوْ لانَ الْحَدِيدُ الْمُصَفَّحُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَإِنَّ الصُّخُورَ الصُّمَّ لانَتْ بِكَفِّهِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَإِنَّ الْحَصَى فِي كَفِّهِ لَيُسَبِّحُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِنْ كَانَ مُوسَى أَنْبَعَ الْمَاءَ مِنَ الْحَصَى<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَمِنْ كَفِّهِ قَدْ أَصْبَحَ الْمَاءُ يَطْفَحُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَإِنْ كَانَتْ الرِّيحُ الرُّخَاءُ مُطِيعَةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>سُلَيْمَانَ لا تَأْلُو تَرُوحُ وَتَسْرَحُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>